spark.spi
Class BaseCommand

java.lang.Object
  spark.spi.BaseCommand
All Implemented Interfaces:
Closeable, Command
public abstract class BaseCommand
extends Object
implements Command

Base implementation for implementors of Command. This class manages the Connection that created the Command, the command string, a closed flag, a timeout, and the binding list.
